'''莫克加迪·卡斯特爾·塞曼亞'''{{tsl|en|Order_of_Ikhamanga|天堂鸟金勋章|OIB}}（{{lang-en|Mokgadi Caster Semenya}}，{{bd|1991年|1月7日||}}），是曾于[[800米赛跑|800米赛跑]]中获得两枚[[奧林匹克運動會獎牌|奥运会金牌]]与三次[[世界田径锦标赛|世界田径锦标赛]]的[[南非|南非]]女子中長跑運動員。她首先于[[2009年世界田径锦标赛|2009年世界田径锦标赛]]中赢得金牌，然后先后于[[2016年夏季奧林匹克運動會田徑女子800公尺比賽|2016年奥运会]]和[[2017年世界田徑錦標賽|2017年世界田徑錦標賽]]获得金牌，亦于2017年在[[1500米賽跑|1500米賽跑]]中获铜牌。在{{tsl|en|Mariya Savinova|玛利亚·萨维诺娃}}因[[表現增強物質|兴奋剂]]被取消资格后，她获得[[2011年世界田徑錦標賽|2011年世界田徑錦標賽]]和[[2012年夏季奧林匹克運動會田徑女子800公尺比賽|2012年奥运会]]金牌。

塞曼亚是[[雙性人|间性人]]女性，于[[性別指定|出生时被指定为女性]]<ref name=BC>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/africa/8215112.stm|title=Birth certificate backs SA gender|date=21 August 2009|work=BBC News|access-date=21 August 2009|archive-date=2018-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180629034036/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/africa/8215112.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，具有[[XY性别决定系统|XY染色体]]和天然{{tsl|en|Hyperandrogenism|高雄激素血症|升高的睾酮水平}}。<ref>{{cite web |last1=Ingle |first1=Sean |title=Caster Semenya accuses IAAF of using her as a ‘guinea pig experiment’ |url=https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2019/jun/18/caster-semenya-iaaf-athletics-guinea-pig |website=The Guardian |access-date=24 May 2021 |date=19 June 2019 |archive-date=2021-04-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210425083252/https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2019/jun/18/caster-semenya-iaaf-athletics-guinea-pig |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Swiss court confirms Semenya cannot compete without hormone-suppressing treatment |url=https://www.france24.com/en/20200908-swiss-court-confirms-semenya-cannot-compete-without-hormone-suppressing-treatment |website=[[Agence_France-Presse|Agence France-Presse]] |access-date=24 May 2021 |date=8 September 2020 |archive-date=2021-08-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210802151222/https://www.france24.com/en/20200908-swiss-court-confirms-semenya-cannot-compete-without-hormone-suppressing-treatment |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Imray |first1=Gerald |title=Semenya taking case to European Court of Human Rights |url=https://apnews.com/article/europe-cape-town-africa-south-africa-2020-tokyo-olympics-c87dd02056cb8b893941cbbfaf31e752 |website=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]] |access-date=24 May 2021 |date=25 February 2021 |archive-date=2021-06-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210620012323/https://apnews.com/article/europe-cape-town-africa-south-africa-2020-tokyo-olympics-c87dd02056cb8b893941cbbfaf31e752 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
她于2009年在世界田径锦标赛上获得冠军后被要求进行{{tsl|en|Sex_verification_in_sports|体育中的性别验证|性别验证}}，并在次年被允许继续比赛。<ref name=ReturnTrack>{{cite news |url=https://www.google.com/hostednews/ap/article/ALeqM5hMudI8ByYmbiNVB4ofKjep_IT_kQD9GPJLSO0 |title=Semenya cleared to return to track immediately |access-date=6 July 2010 |agency=Associated Press |date=6 July 2010 |url-status=yes |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100709190844/https://www.google.com/hostednews/ap/article/ALeqM5hMudI8ByYmbiNVB4ofKjep_IT_kQD9GPJLSO0 |archive-date=2010-07-09 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2010/jul/06/caster-semenya-iaaf-clearance|title=Caster Semenya may return to track this month after IAAF clearance|access-date=6 July 2010|work=The Guardian|date=6 July 2010|location=London|first=Anna|last=Kessel|archive-date=2021-08-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210802145709/https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2010/jul/06/caster-semenya-iaaf-clearance|dead-url=no}}</ref>
于2019年，新的[[世界田径|世界田径]]规则开始生效，导致像塞曼亚一样的女性无法继续在女子组别中参加[[400米赛跑|400米]]、[[800米赛跑|800米]]和[[1500米賽跑|1500米賽跑]]，除非服用药物以抑制睾酮水平。2021年，她就这些限制向[[欧洲人权法院|欧洲人权法院]]提出上诉。<ref>{{cite news |last1=IMRAY |first1=GERALD |title=Semenya taking case to European Court of Human Rights |url=https://abcnews.go.com/Sports/wireStory/semenya-taking-case-european-court-human-rights-76106450?cid=clicksource_4380645_15_hero_headlines_headlines_hed |access-date=February 25, 2021 |work=ABC News |agency=AP |date=February 25, 2021 |language=en |archive-date=2021-08-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210802145654/https://abcnews.go.com/Sports/wireStory/semenya-taking-case-european-court-human-rights-76106450?cid=clicksource_4380645_15_hero_headlines_headlines_hed |dead-url=no }}</ref>

